         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper we construct minimal cubature formulae of trigonometric degree: we obtain explicit formulae for low dimensions of arbitrary degree and for low degrees in all dimensions. A useful tool is a closed form expression for the reproducing kernels in two dimensions.</p>
          </abstract>
